)

Default "less than" comparison operator of states of this RTNO; the order is arbitrary (a simple comparison of the pointers of both states), this operator is required for building sets of states or tuples containing states

Template Parameters
TagInputthe input type of the tags of this RTNO
TagOutputthe output type of the tags of this RTNO
Parameters
q1a state of this RTNO
q2another state of this RTNO
Returns
whether q1 is less than q2 (q1's pointer is less than q2's)
